+# TurnerAI Implementation Plan
+
+This scaffold maps the original Genesis Engine AI prompt into a practical starter architecture.
+
+## Delivered in this commit
+
+- **Web-based 3D editor foundation** (React + Three.js viewport, hierarchy, inspector, asset browser, AI prompt panels).
+- **Node.js API foundation** with JWT auth, subscription tiers, generation quota gating, queue-like async generation jobs, export restrictions, dashboard payload, project encryption utility, and Stripe webhook signature validation.
+- **Tier modeling** for Builder, Pro, Studio, Creator Elite matching requested pricing and capability boundaries.
+- **AI endpoints** for scene generation, game logic generation, NPC generation, and Studio-tier multiplayer template generation.
+
+## Next build phases
+
+1. Replace fake generation payloads with actual model/script generation workers.
+2. Persist data in Postgres + object storage (S3/GCS).
+3. Move queue execution to Redis/BullMQ and add abuse/rate-limiting middleware.
+4. Integrate real Stripe checkout and customer portal.
+5. Add import/export packagers for Roblox/Unity/Unreal file formats.
 
EOF
)
